         I'm a firm believer that if there is only one person behind the keyboard than they should get one roll. While it is true macros are your friend, there is only one person behind the keyboard. Most guilds Ive been in have a loot council. If your adding more to the raid then youll get more out of it. </P><P>Anyway, thats just my 2 plat.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
